SPDX-License-Identifier: CC0-1.0 OR MIT

This repository wraps the upstream Occam ARC-AGI-3 solver (MIT, Sean Donahoe)
with the hardseal-trace v0.2.0 cryptographic reasoning-trace primitive
(Apache-2.0, Hardseal LLC).

The wrapper code in this repo (`hardseal_occam/`, the Kaggle submission
notebook, the build/runner scripts, NOTICE.md, README.md) is dual-licensed
under CC0-1.0 OR MIT at the recipient's option, per ARC Prize 2026 contest
rules. See NOTICE.md for the full provenance and license map.

